{"id": 1958, "genre": 1001, "title": "对于“把钱花在刀刃上”，你有哪些心得？", "description": "关于哪些东西随便买买就行，哪些东西一定精挑细选，我是有一套的。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2872, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171016101323LvE8U9w3oSnAdu6z.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-17T03:00:30Z", "options": [{"id": 242176, "content": "给父母花不在乎，自己花时那个纠结那个掂量", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157433}, {"id": 242178, "content": "给自己花钱不心疼，给别人花一点也不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153021}, {"id": 242179, "content": "吃的不省，穿上很省，医药费不省，结果每次都没办法好好地买东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183815}, {"id": 242180, "content": "淘单", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848921}, {"id": 242437, "content": "出国旅游之所以没有买买买\n心里想的都是回国美容卡健身卡都等着我续费呢?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084594}, {"id": 264710, "content": "对于给自己花钱不心疼的人同样花钱不心疼，就是花在刀刃上了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853433}, {"id": 242183, "content": "买东西要么不买，决定了要买就一定要选择好的、贵的，要不然买了便宜的就容易产生不满意不喜欢的感觉，导致使用一段时间就废置而浪费。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096939}, {"id": 243207, "content": "天天吃15块的饭觉得有点贵 天天喝一杯15块的奶茶毫不犹豫", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794487}, {"id": 242184, "content": "一般把钱投入近期最大的爱好上，其他的就缩减一下，然后总是让自己少吃点乱七八糟的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157485}, {"id": 242185, "content": "想到把钱存下来以后要干大事", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 243209, "content": "装修基础设施", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163878}, {"id": 242186, "content": "在实体店一般看中了（当然是在自己经济承受能力范围内）就买，在某宝可以逛很久也决定不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106579}, {"id": 242188, "content": "对于购买前会纠结10分钟以上的一律不买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080730}, {"id": 242190, "content": "那个给女朋友花钱不心疼的，你还缺女朋友吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663052}, {"id": 242191, "content": "每种款式都要有一两件拿的出手的，其他的简单舒服就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157508}, {"id": 247823, "content": "生活处处是刀刃-.-", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181901}, {"id": 242192, "content": "有能力的时候，都要最好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075772}, {"id": 242960, "content": "看病时从不计较，买游戏时处处小心。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154469}, {"id": 242193, "content": "用在健康上的钱不吝啬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 242195, "content": "自己怎么都能对付，和朋友家人一起就尽量做到最好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811061}, {"id": 242196, "content": "当然是自己的身体最重要。牙刷，牙膏这是最最必要买贵的，跟你一辈子的就是它说严重点，幸福生活的一半就靠它啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087927}, {"id": 243221, "content": "为亲朋好友花钱不在乎 给自己买份30块钱的饭矛盾起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164219}, {"id": 242198, "content": "没有存够养老钱分分钟觉得自己老了会饿死！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126107}, {"id": 242200, "content": "小学的时候就买书不眨眼，初中每次一两百的买回去，高中同样。现在大学，会稍微克制一点，不过遇到喜欢的虽然贵，但并不犹豫。(家境不是很好，然而买书就是毫不吝啬)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153469}, {"id": 242201, "content": "经常吃泡面，买起皮肤却一套一套的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133461}, {"id": 242202, "content": "股票，债券和基金", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 242458, "content": "当你在买想买的东西的时候犹豫了，那就不是真的想买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158657}, {"id": 243227, "content": "很少花钱，什么都计算，但是长期找不到就会乱花", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164318}, {"id": 242204, "content": "从来都管理不好钱的我，真的不知道什么叫花在刀刃上?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1149297}, {"id": 242205, "content": "一双鞋子基本能买两套衣服了，买衣服只看实惠，买鞋子注重质量", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136667}, {"id": 242206, "content": "给孩子花钱不心疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147413}, {"id": 242207, "content": "热水器和马桶 浴室里的东西真特么不能用质量低的！！【住在租房里的人捶墙中】", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 242208, "content": "在书店看到心仪的书以后，再去亚马逊上看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912090}, {"id": 242976, "content": "处处都是刀刃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161545}, {"id": 242209, "content": "饭可以不吃，但咖啡必须一天一杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979690}, {"id": 242210, "content": "使用率决定性价比，so每天都用的东西值得买好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157618}, {"id": 242212, "content": "衣服可能可以差点。但鞋子一定得买好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933325}, {"id": 243236, "content": "别十块十块的花,生活费都是这么败没的能不花就不花,除了看书,化妆品跟衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140669}, {"id": 242213, "content": "虽少必精……", "image": "img/option/option/20171017190425Ts43nr6Rh2bzf0pU", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157629}, {"id": 242214, "content": "生活处处是刀刃", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157633}, {"id": 242215, "content": "用app计算每天花多少钱，剩下的积蓄买p2p，当你每天看着积蓄持续上涨，你就有动力存钱，限制自己花钱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058308}, {"id": 242216, "content": "个人恩格尔系数无限接近1，钱全都用来吃了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156102}, {"id": 242217, "content": "鞋子要买好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156838}, {"id": 242219, "content": "选适合的 不买贵的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134047}, {"id": 243244, "content": "上学时买牛奶酸奶的钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080073}, {"id": 242221, "content": "<img>", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157644}, {"id": 242222, "content": "货比三家，然后选一个不是特别便宜的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129963}, {"id": 242223, "content": "千金难买心头好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493367}, {"id": 242224, "content": "手贱就要点开淘宝，默默输入支付密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145741}, {"id": 242225, "content": "给爸妈买东西不心疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060333}]}